    <abstract id="aspace_d05b9e5a40b676aed9e62bf0b454fcfd">The An American Family Collection consists of 12 one-hour episodes of the 12-hour documentary, "An American Family," that debuted on PBS-TV in early 1973. It consists of 12 DVDs.</abstract>
    <langmaterial id="aspace_d3b4225465ec767ad2ec6e3ca74e77cd">Materials are in English.</langmaterial>
  </did>
  <arrangement id="aspace_87536e9db64dc8dd0a5ca81ee0d85e3d">
    <head>Arrangement</head>
<p>The episodes are arranged in one series, in the order in which they originally aired on PBS-TV in 1973.</p>  </arrangement>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_55a70903d0713b63a57295dfa5085422">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>The collection is comprised of 12 one-hour episodes that document the Loud's day-to-day life during seven months of 1971.</p>  </scopecontent>
